Jenkins Views (Job Organization):
---------------------------------
    problem: large projects --> 100+ jobs
    difficult to navigate

    solution: views help group jobs logically

    Create View:
    ------------
        click + (New View)
        enter name (e.g facebook project)
        select List View
        add required jobs
        save

    Example:
    --------
    View Name: Facebook project
    Jobs: FB-Login, FB-payment

    View Name: Maven project
    Jobs: Build, Test

    Features:
    ----------
        - easy navigation
        - organize jobs by project/team
        - no limit on number of views

    Limitations:
    ------------
        - No sub views
        - No search bar in dashboard